sequenceDiagram
  participant W as Signal Worker
  participant PM as Polymarket REST
  participant DR as Deribit API
  participant MP as Mapping Service
  participant DB as Postgres

  W->>MP: load mappings
  W->>DR: get_index_price (spot)
  loop per market
    W->>PM: get orderbook
    W->>DR: get_order_book (mark_iv)
    W->>W: implied + theoretical + spread
    W->>DB: insert signal
  end
